com.opendxl.databus.entities.internal

Class DatabusMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opendxl.databus.entities.internal.DatabusMessage

  • public class DatabusMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    It represents the message sent thru Databus. It contains a Headers and payload as byte[]

    This class is for internal use of Databus-SDK. It is created and kept as a member of ConsumerRecord and it is used when the Databus-SDK's user invoke DatabusProducer.send() method
